OL,5, Begging on the streets is to be clamped
OL,6, down on by police across south Wales.  
OL,8,FOperation Luscombe has been running in 
OL,9,FMerthyr Tydfil since 2020 but is now   
OL,10,Fbeing rolled out across the area,      
OL,11,Fincluding Cardiff and Swansea.         
OL,13,FSouth Wales Police said it aimed to    
OL,14,Fhelp homeless people access help and   
OL,15,Fsupport.                               
OL,17,FHowever some councillors said the      
OL,18,Fmeasures could be seen as "hostile" and
OL,19,Frisked criminalising and isolating some
OL,20,Fof the most vulnerable people.         
